                    </hi>
                    <note n="63" xml:id="d248fn63">This Report was discussed by the Council of
                        Foreign Ministers at its 42nd Meeting, July 12, 1946. For the decision of
                        the Council with respect to the claims by Greece and Yugoslavia to the
