                <p>3. The Naval Committee failed to reach agreement, and, therefore, asks the
                    Ministers to decide the following questions: <list>
                        <label>(<hi rend="italic">a</hi>)</label>
                        <item>Should the principle of equality of treatment be applied to Yugoslavia
                            and Greece?</item>
                        <label>(<hi rend="italic">b</hi>)</label>
                        <item>If not, who should be given the cruiser “Savoia”—Yugoslavia or
                            Greece—or should it be put up for allocation between the Four
                            Powers.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
